deck: BAO Publishing is one of Italy's leading graphic novel publishers
description:
BAO Publishing is one of Italy's leading graphic novel publishers. Founded in 2009, it has since (2015) published over 250 titles, and is the Italian home of the likes of Jeff Smith, Terry Moore, Scott McCloud and Alan Moore's creator owned works. Among its original production are the complete works of Zerocalcare, constantly at the top of the bookstore charts for graphic novels, having sold well over two hundred thousand copies in two years.

From: http://www.baopublishing.it/chi-siamo

Facebook: www.facebook.com/baopublishing

Twitter: www.twitter.com/baopublishing

Instagram: @baopublishing
